id: pm-j2ig
title: "Agent context & bulk-ops primitives: incremental date filters, search --status, --ids targeting, close-many"
description: "Deliver four interlocking agent-facing CLI/SDK primitives that serve project-management=context-management: pm list --updated-after/--updated-before/--created-after/--created-before (pm-y138/pm-ankr), pm search --status parity (pm-ec4s/pm-arew), pm update-many --ids explicit ID allowlist (pm-1h99), and pm close-many bulk-close with runClose semantics + dry-run + checkpoint/rollback (pm-i17g/pm-9mjw)."
type: Plan
status: closed
priority: 1
tags[5]: agent-ux,"area:cli",bulk-ops,living-map,query
