  "2026-06-04T16:26:22.710Z",codex-sdk-contract-subagent,"SDK/contract verification subagent evidence: reviewed branch commit 7504da28 for agent context + bulk-ops primitives against SDK/CLI/MCP package-author surfaces. Findings: no bounded SDK/contract bug found. Verified close-many is exported from src/cli/commands/index.ts, registered as core command/action, listed in PM_CORE_COMMAND_NAMES/PM_TOOL_ACTIONS, exposed through pm contracts --command close-many --flags-only --json and pm contracts --action close-many --schema-only --json with filter date-window fields, --ids, reason/resolution/expectedResult/actualResult/validateClose/dryRun/rollback/noCheckpoint parameters. Verified update-many contracts expose date-window filter fields + --ids, list contracts expose updated/created date-window filters, search contracts expose --status, and pm search --status opne returns strict did-you-mean usage guidance. Commands run: pnpm build; pm contracts --command close-many --flags-only --json; pm close-many --help --json; pm contracts --command search --flags-only --json; pm contracts --action close-many --schema-only --json; pm contracts --action update-many --schema-only --json; pm list --help --json; pm search pm-j2ig --status opne --json (expected exit 2); node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/status-normalization.spec.ts tests/unit/list-command.spec.ts tests/unit/search-command.spec.ts tests/unit/update-many-command.spec.ts tests/unit/close-command.spec.ts (140 passed); temp-project dist/cli.js smoke covering list --updated-after, search --status open, update-many --ids apply, close-many --ids --dry-run (passed). Note: an attempted temp smoke with pm init --name and pm list --ids correctly failed as unsupported current contracts; reran with pm init and mutation-scoped --ids. Changed files by this subagent: none besides this pm evidence comment."
  "2026-06-04T16:27:53.935Z",codex-gh-release-subagent,"GitHub/release/security verification subagent evidence (2026-06-04T16:30Z, branch cli-incremental-context-and-bulk-ops-20260604):\n- GitHub live state: gh repo view => unbraind/pm-cli public repo, default branch main; gh pr list --state open => []; gh issue list --state open => []. Current branch is 1 commit ahead of origin/main and has no open branch workflow runs yet.\n- Recent CI/release state: latest main CI run 26945147068 success; latest main Docs run 26945085852 success; Nightly Validation schedule run 26939971636 success. Latest Auto Release schedule run 26936604085 failed at Run auto release pipeline because SENTRY_PERSONAL_ADMIN_TOKEN was empty; Release workflow latest runs 26804564260 and 26741550574 also failed after dispatch on Jun 2/Jun 1. Latest GitHub release remains v2026.5.31 (2026-05-31T06:52:03Z). This is environment/secret readiness, not a code regression in this branch.\n- Security state: gh api dependabot alerts state=open => []; vulnerability-alerts endpoint returned HTTP 204; secret-scanning alerts state=open => []; repo security advisories state=open => []; code-scanning alerts returned 404 no analysis found plus missing admin:repo_hook scope, so no code-scanning evidence is available through current auth.\n- Dependency state: pnpm audit --audit-level moderate => No known vulnerabilities found. pnpm outdated reports only commander 14.0.3 -> 15.0.0, but npm view commander@15.0.0 engines => node >=22.12.0 while README/package/workflows still support/run Node 20. I kept/restored commander at ^14.0.3 and refreshed pnpm-lock.yaml to avoid a release compatibility break for CI, Docs, Nightly, and Auto Release Node 20 jobs.\n- pm-changelog state: npm view pm-changelog version => 2026.6.4; pnpm changelog:pm:check installed/activated pm-changelog 2026.6.4 and reported CHANGELOG.md unchanged, item_count 961, check true. .agents/pm/extensions/.managed-extensions.json timestamp refreshed from the latest install.\n- Verification passed after the dependency compatibility fix: pnpm audit --audit-level moderate, pnpm build, pnpm changelog:pm:check.\nCommands run included: gh pr list, gh issue list, gh run list, gh run view 26936604085 --log-failed, gh release list, gh api dependabot/code-scanning/secret-scanning/vulnerability/security-advisory endpoints, pnpm audit, pnpm outdated, npm view pm-changelog version, npm view commander@15.0.0 engines, pnpm add commander@^14.0.3, pnpm build, pnpm changelog:pm:check."
