plan_decisions[2]{ts,author,decision}:
  "2026-06-04T16:04:13.352Z",maintainer-agent,"Implemented all 4 primitives + shared core modules (status-filter, mutation-checkpoint) + full wiring (commander, normalize, cli-contracts flag+param+schema, enum-contracts, MCP server action, contracts core map, completion bash/zsh/fish, help-content, telemetry mutation sets). Date-window filters use the shared signed-relative resolver (-2h=past, +1d=future; m=months, no minutes unit) — primary use is ISO timestamps for 'changed since last window'. close-many requires >=1 filter (never matches all) and a shared --reason; skips already-terminal unless --force; checkpoint+rollback via shared core. Manually smoke-tested all four end-to-end in temp dirs (dry-run/apply/rollback/skip-terminal/did-you-mean all verified)."
  "2026-06-04T16:17:58.613Z",maintainer-agent,"All 4 primitives shipped + 7 pm items closed (pm-y138/pm-ankr/pm-ec4s/pm-arew/pm-1h99/pm-i17g/pm-9mjw). Full suite: 2254 tests pass, 100% coverage; static + docs + secret gates green. Test-author subagent added 78 command-level cases across list/search/close specs; lead added status-filter + mutation-checkpoint (100%) + update-many --ids cases. Docs (COMMANDS/AGENT_GUIDE/help-content) + completions (bash/zsh/fish) updated. Next: regenerate CHANGELOG, commit, PR, bot-review loop."
